  "name": "RPlog_Battle_of_Gyndine",
  "title": "The Rapier Against the Inquisitor",
  "summary": "A New Republic strike force jumps into the Gyndine system, and the Mon Calamari cruisers Rapier and Promise are tasked with pinning down the Imperial Star Destroyer Inquisitor while the rest of the fleet attacks the planet's Golan battlestation. Rasi, commanding the Rapier, trades calculated broadsides with the Inquisitor's wry, hands-on captain Valerius, both men maneuvering for shield advantage as bombers make repeated runs. Amid the capital duel, Imperial pilot Jonas Alsten and the Zabrak X-wing pilot Ghost 8 fight a personal, recurring dogfight that ends inconclusively. The Inquisitor's shields finally collapse under sustained fire, but with the Golan station crippled and the Republic flagship Bluegrass damaged, the Republic warships break off and retreat to hyperspace, leaving the engagement a costly, even draw.",
